Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.52,0:36:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,socialism.\NYou see the the the male, the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.11,0:36:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional male, you get what you get\Nin the world by your own effort. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.35,0:36:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Period. What you get is what you worked\Nfor and earned through your own sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and blood. That's the paternalistic. The\Nmaternal maternalistic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.72,0:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is more politically expressed. The\Nmother does not differentiate. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.96,0:36:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,her children she treats equally. All of\Nthem. All of them are deserving because
