Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything uh to get\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.92,0:37:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,uh and our society I think is very\Nwellbalanced where through your own
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.52,0:37:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,effort and self-sacrifice\Nyou move ahead and also
