Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.72,0:37:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody. So it's sort of hard to hard\Nto hard to starve to death in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.28,0:38:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to really work at it because\Nsomebody will pick up pick up for you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.80,0:38:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and lead you to the nearest welfare\Nassistance. So in my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't express opinions much, but when\NI do, I say in my opinion, my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.96,0:38:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,our country is a is a wonderful balance\Nof the maternal and the paternal, the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.00,0:38:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,masculine and the feminine of blended\Ntogether and working together because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.07,0:38:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,each one serves the other. All right. We\Nsee the carnival in our world of of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.28,0:38:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,causes, you know,\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.92,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of elitism\Nand there's a there's always a passing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.80,0:38:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fed like I say, save the hippopotamus or\Nsave the reindeer or save somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.83,0:38:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Environmentalism gets a very big push.\NAnd of course, you can justify anything
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.35,0:39:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with historical revisionism. What you do\Nis you reinterpret history in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.56,0:39:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and what gets juiced the most is being\Nthe victim. People love to be the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,victim. It's enormous competition to be\Nthe victim. And if you can't find any
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.76,0:39:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,reason to be a victim, that's because\Nyou haven't gone back far enough in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.59,0:39:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,history.\NIn history, everyone here, everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.16,0:39:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was enslaved.\NYou know the antecedence of every single
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.56,0:39:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,person sitting here.\NWhat I just said is true. Resist. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.76,0:39:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because slavery was an evolutionary\Nstage of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.88,0:39:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, the Vikings captured\Neverybody and killed everybody. The gods
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.59,0:39:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,killed everybody. The Vikings, the Huns,\Neverybody killed everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then some enterprising smarty got you\Ncould sell these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.56,0:39:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, when you So they stopped killing\Nthem because now they could be sold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.59,0:40:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So slavery was worldwide. Worldwide in\Nancient Rome almost everybody was a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,slave. Nine out of 10 people ancient\NEgypt, ancient Greece, etc. So therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.76,0:40:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it was normal. It was not immoral in\Nthat world. Historically, it was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.00,0:40:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, it was a lot better to be\Nenslaved than slaughtered because in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.07,0:40:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,those days, the Vikings chopped your\Nhead head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.92,0:40:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, as parts of the world would like to\Ndo still. Anyway, if you lost, they
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.48,0:40:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,chopped off your head. Chopped off your\Nhead. So, it was better that you got
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.59,0:40:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sold off. At least you got to live. And\Nif you live, sooner or later you would
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.48,0:40:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,find some level of happiness and you\Nmight escape, etc. But it's better to be
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.83,0:40:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,captured and enslaved and allowed to\Nlive than having your head cut off. When
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.92,0:41:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your head's cut off, that cuts your\Noptions short.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.04,0:41:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see all these uh isms,\Nexhibitionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.44,0:41:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um the desire to be famous, you know, is\Nso predominant.
