Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.31,0:42:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional.\NWhat you do is you get fame and fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.68,0:42:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and you sell your soul to get it. So a\Ngood part of society is willing to sell
