Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.59,0:43:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, now that you can,\Nuh, get yourself on international
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.52,0:43:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,television at the flip of a button while\Nyou're driving with one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.48,0:43:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've looked at relativism versus\Nabsolutism before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.20,0:43:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,uh relativis relativism is actually a\Nvariety of the Marxist doctrine Marxism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of victim and perpetrator\Nvictor and perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.31,0:43:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes uh actually from intellectual\Nerror relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.92,0:43:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A thing is only true if I believe it to\Nbe true. So in relativism is the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.83,0:43:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite of absolutism.\NAnd I notice some people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.44,0:44:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,warn readers of of anything I've\Nwritten. Warning, he's an absolutist.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.31,0:44:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning, he's an absolutist. Watch out.\NYou're not a relativist because truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.16,0:44:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not what subject to your opinion. Uh\Ntruth is so no matter what your opinion
