Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.24,0:48:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,created, you know, uh to handle your\Ninfantile feelings of what you like and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.52,0:48:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what you don't like. And people might be\Noffended. People are offended by
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.40,0:48:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.\Nyou you wouldn't be able to speak or
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.00,0:48:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,talk or leave the house because you're\Ngoing to offend somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.88,0:48:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this preoccupation that somebody\Nmight be offended, every day you see
