Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.40,0:48:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm I I belong to an offender protest\Ngroup
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.68,0:48:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I don't give a P whether you're\Noffended or not about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.31,0:48:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Being offended is your problem.\NNo, I am offended by they're being
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.24,0:49:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,offended by everything. You can't speak\Nof anything that some group doesn't put
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.48,0:49:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,up a protest sign\Nthat somebody's first in line
